    'Luksusowy': 'Luksusowy is a brand of windshield washers providing clean and bright glass in any weather. Products are distinguished by high quality and cleaning efficiency.\n\nLuksusowy windshield washers provide excellent visibility and protection from contamination, making driving safer and more comfortable.',
    'Autoglas': 'Autoglas is a brand of windshield washers offering quality fluids for effective cleaning of windshield and side glass of the car. Products are developed to ensure optimal visibility in various operating conditions.\n\nAutoglas windshield washers provide clean glass and contribute to road safety.',
    'ADICS': 'ADICS is a brand of windshield washers providing reliable and effective car glass cleaning. Products are distinguished by high quality and affordable price.\n\nADICS windshield washers provide clean glass and excellent visibility in any weather.',
    'QUANTUM-washer': 'QUANTUM is a premium class windshield washer brand. Products provide high-quality glass cleaning and excellent visibility.\n\nQUANTUM windshield washers are distinguished by reliability and efficiency, making them an ideal choice for car owners who value quality.',
    'Plax-washer': 'Plax is a brand of windshield washers providing quality car glass cleaning. Products are distinguished by efficiency and reliability.\n\nPlax windshield washers provide clean glass and excellent visibility, making driving safer and more comfortable.',
    'RONDEX': 'RONDEX is a brand of windshield washers providing quality car glass cleaning. Products are distinguished by efficiency and reliability.\n\nRONDEX windshield washers provide clean glass and excellent visibility, making driving safer and more comfortable.',
    'Аляsка': 'ALASKA is a brand of windscreen washers that provides effective glass cleaning in extreme temperature conditions. The products are designed to work reliably in any season. \n\nALASKA windscreen washers ensure clean glass and excellent visibility even in the harshest frosts and hot summer days.',
